{"word":"ἐπικλύζω","slug":"ἐπικλύζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπικλύζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ύσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to overflow</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to deluge, swamp</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἐπ. τινὰ κακοῖς</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, also, <i>to sweep away, liquidate</i> the expenses, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}